title: gauntlets of water walking
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While wearing these steel gauntlets, you can stand on your hands on any liquid surface as though it were solid ground. You can walk on your hands to traverse the surface, but if you fall, you fall into the liquid and must begin swimming.